 Your status help
 ----------------

 Change handle - lets you change your handle.

 Graphics on/off - this lets you toggle whether you want ANSI graphics
displayed, providing the BBS is configured to allow them.

 Help - this stuff.

 Password change - allows you to change your logon password.

 Quit - returns to the main menu.
 
 System status - displays current information on the state of the system.

 X-pert user mode - toggles the X-pert user mode on or off.  When on, the
X-pert user mode will shorten some system prompts.

 Your status - displays your current statistics.
